SUMMARY:Game Your Future Conference
DESCRIPTION:This is the 4th annual Game Your Future is a conference\, an event organized by Maryland-regional developer groups at the Baltimore Convention Center.  It brings an experience similar to the Game Developers Conference (GDC) to the East Coast to fill the void of a more accessible event for our East Coast devs who want something near where they live.
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/game-your-future-conference/
LOCATION:Baltimore Convention Center\, 1 W Pratt Street\, Baltimore\, MD\, 21201\, United States
END:VEVENT
